          <p>Complete strip-out and refurbishment of your existing bathroom. New bath, toilet, basin, shower and all tiling. We handle everything from removing the old bathroom to the final grout and seal.</p>
          <span class="service-type-price">Labour from £2,500 · Supply and fit from £4,500</span>
        </div>
        <div class="service-type-card">
          <div class="service-type-icon">EN S</div>
