        </div>
        <div class="service-type-card">
          <div class="service-type-icon">WET</div>
          <h3>Wet Room Installation</h3>
          <p>Full wet room with waterproof tanking, linear or central drain, wall-to-wall tiling and frameless glass panels. Requires specialist installation to prevent water damage. Our most popular premium option.</p>
          <span class="service-type-price">From £3,500 supply and fit</span>
        </div>
        <div class="service-type-card">
          <div class="service-type-icon">SHWR</div>
          <h3>Shower Installation and Replacement</h3>
          <p>Electric shower, power shower, mixer shower or thermostatic bar valve installation. New enclosure, tray or wet wall boarding. Walk-in shower conversions from bath to shower.</p>
          <span class="service-type-price">From £400 supply and fit</span>
        </div>
        <div class="service-type-card">
          <div class="service-type-icon">ACC</div>
          <h3>Accessible and Level-Access Bathrooms</h3>
          <p>Bathroom adaptations for elderly or disabled Liverpool residents. Walk-in shower, level-access shower tray, grab rails, raised toilet seat and fold-down shower seats. All installed with care and respect.</p>
          <span class="service-type-price">From £2,500 supply and fit</span>
        </div>
        <div class="service-type-card">
          <div class="service-type-icon">FIT</div>
          <h3>Labour-Only Bathroom Fitting</h3>
          <p>Already chosen your bathroom suite from B&Q, Victorian Plumbing, Bathstore or another retailer? We provide competitive labour-only quotes to fit your chosen products to the highest standard.</p>
          <span class="service-type-price">Labour from £2,500 for a full bathroom</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRICING -->
  <section class="section-pad" style="background:var(--bg);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Bathroom Fitting Prices Liverpool</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Honest price ranges so you can plan your budget. Written fixed-price quote provided at the free survey. The <a href="https://www.checkatrade.com/Search/Bathroom-Fitter/in/Liverpool" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--navy);">Checkatrade average for Liverpool bathroom fitting is £1,780 to £4,865</a>.</p>

      <div class="bathroom-type-grid">
        <div class="bathroom-type-card">
          <h3>Full Bathroom Renovation</h3>
