          <div class="bathroom-price-tag">Labour: from £2,500 · Supply and fit: from £4,500</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bathroom-type-card">
          <h3>En Suite Installation</h3>
          <p>New en suite in existing bedroom space. All plumbing, fitting and tiling included.</p>
          <div class="bathroom-price-tag">Labour: from £2,000 · Supply and fit: from £3,500</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bathroom-type-card">
          <h3>Wet Room</h3>
          <p>Full wet room with tanking, drain and frameless glass. Specialist installation required.</p>
          <div class="bathroom-price-tag">Supply and fit: from £3,500</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bathroom-type-card">
          <h3>Shower Installation</h3>
          <p>New shower installation or replacement. Enclosure, tray and all plumbing included.</p>
          <div class="bathroom-price-tag">Supply and fit: from £400</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bathroom-type-card">
          <h3>Accessible Bathroom</h3>
          <p>Level-access shower, grab rails, raised toilet and all adaptations. Caring and professional installation.</p>
          <div class="bathroom-price-tag">Supply and fit: from £2,500</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bathroom-type-card">
          <h3>Bathroom Refresh</h3>
          <p>Replacing toilet, basin or taps without a full renovation. Individual fixture replacement and replumbing.</p>
          <div class="bathroom-price-tag">From £300 per fixture</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:4px solid var(--orange);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;margin-top:1.5rem;text-align:center;">
        <strong style="color:var(--navy);display:block;margin-bottom:0.35rem;">Why we do not quote over the phone</strong>
        <p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.9rem;margin:0;">Bathroom fitting costs depend on the size of the room, position of existing pipework, wall construction, access to soil stacks and your chosen fixtures. A phone quote cannot account for these variables accurately. We visit your Liverpool property, assess the full picture and provide a written fixed-price quote covering everything before any commitment is made.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
