        </div>
        <div class="included-row">
          <span class="included-tick">✓</span>
          <div><strong>Accessories and fixtures</strong><span>Towel rails, toilet roll holders, mirror fixings, shower trays and screens all fitted and sealed to a professional finish.</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="included-row">
          <span class="included-tick">✓</span>
