          <div><strong>Clean-up on completion</strong><span>We clean the bathroom thoroughly before handover. You see the finished result, not the mess of the installation process.</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="included-row">
          <span class="included-tick">✓</span>
          <div><strong>12-month workmanship guarantee</strong><span>All our bathroom work carries a 12-month guarantee. If anything fails due to our workmanship we come back and fix it at no charge.</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section class="section-pad eicr-process-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 style="text-align:center;">How Our Liverpool Bathroom Installation Works</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">From first call to a fully fitted bathroom, here is what to expect from our managed service.</p>
      <div class="process-steps">
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Free Site Survey</h3>
            <p>We visit your Liverpool property, measure the bathroom and discuss your requirements and budget. We advise on layout, fixtures and tiles and provide a written fixed-price quote.</p>
            <span class="step-note">Free. No obligation.</span>
          </div>
