          <div class="faq-body">
            <p>A standard full bathroom renovation takes 7 to 10 working days. A simpler shower installation or partial renovation takes 2 to 4 days. Wet rooms and accessible bathrooms involving structural changes take 10 to 14 days. We confirm the exact timeline at the free survey so you can plan accordingly.</p>
